public boolean checkHost(String host) {
	for (String h : banned) {
		if (h.equals(host))
			return false;
	}
	int num = 0;
	for (String h : connections) {
		if (host.equals(h)) {
			num++;
		}
	}
	if (num > 5) {
		banHost(host, num);
		return false;

	if (checkLog("ipbans", host)) {

	// check ipbans -bakatool
